Class BoxAndWhiskerChart

  • java.lang.Object
    • o3smeasures.plugin.chart.BoxAndWhiskerChart

  • public class BoxAndWhiskerChart
extends java.lang.Object
    Class that implements a Box and Whisker chart with the results of the items measured in the plugin, separeted in internal quality factors. See in http://repositorio.ufla.br/handle/1/10561.
